{"tid":415991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勒索病毒NRansomware要上傳裸照才能解鎖","createTime":"2017-09-27T12:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T12:50:04.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7c0784bdde5a81d4e1004fb3b44860c9bb1f5899","tid":415991,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:14:51.000Z","msg":"勒索病毒NRansomware要上傳裸照才能解鎖<br />\nLawton<br />\n<br />\n以往電腦上的勒索病毒例如 WannaCry 都只是向受害人勒索金錢，或者是 bitcoin。但最近有駭客設計的一款全新勒索病毒，就要求受害人發送 10 張裸照，才能為電腦解鎖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來自 MalwareHunterTeam 的勒索病毒專家，就發放了一些新型勒索病毒「nRansomware」的詳細資料，他們展示了一張中招用戶的畫面截圖。在畫面截圖中可看到，駭客要求用戶登記一個伺服器位處於瑞士的電郵帳戶，然後發送一個電郵給駭客。<br />\n<br />\n駭客在處理好「申請」後，會發給用戶回覆，用戶需要發送最少 10 張裸照給他們。駭客會查核裸照是否屬於受害人本人，經審核之後就會給受害者解鎖密碼。而裸照則會在 deep web 深層網路上販售。所謂 Deep web，就是指一般搜尋器無法找到的內容，相信是一些色情網站的訂購服務。<br />\n<br />\n到目前 nRansomware 仍未有任何解決方法。電腦用戶需要為 OS 升級最新版本或安裝防毒軟件來保護自己。"},{"pid":"f3e00b9e2a2565a28955718b5cc6de98bdd69c18","tid":415991,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:18:01.000Z","msg":"男女通吃？"},{"pid":"44f748f85eed325ca056499c37e0a12908abde79","tid":415991,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:26:05.000Z","msg":"勒索病毒nRansomware要上傳裸照才能解鎖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/415938/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/415938/page/1</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c0207e15755d320284620b040799ce31be0494d4","tid":415991,"uid":94835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:39:46.000Z","msg":"擺十張天真嬌過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b0935ae28b3861ebb7c4c84805979cc777d622","tid":415991,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:41:12.000Z","msg":"有新意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10001e8274aca40132d7352b22e9c55cc51113bc","tid":415991,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:47:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>擺十張天真嬌過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要核實係本人先得"},{"pid":"ead884210485400902ecacae7086308339d6a8c6","tid":415991,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:50:04.000Z","msg":"咁大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}